{{codepointer|Generic Attack}}
'''A_BulletAttack'''

(no parameters)


Performs a [[hitscan]] attack. The amount of bullets fired is specified with the actor's {{c|{{Property|Damage}}}} property. Additionally the {{Property|AttackSound|attack sound}} is being played.

== Examples ==
This is a shotgun zombie. It fires 5 bullets, according to its {{c|Damage}} property.

 ACTOR ShotgunZombie : {{Class|ZombieMan}}
 {
   {{Property|Damage}} 5
   States
   {
   Missile:
     POSS E 10 [[A_FaceTarget]]
     POSS F 8 [[A_BulletAttack]]
     POSS E 8
     Goto See
   }
 }
